dcterms:description: The C-MAPSS dataset contains run-to-failure data of turbofan engines, simulated using a thermodynamic simulation model. It includes information from 21 sensors and 3 operating conditions, composed of four subsets (FD001, FD002, FD003, FD004) that differ in terms of working conditions, fault modes, life spans, and number of engines.
dcterms:title: C-MAPSS Turbofan Engine Dataset
